&lt;/div&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://sachaai.com/images/Articles/Grandfather-No-Inheritance.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
